[
    {
        "text": "Design engineers work hard to solve problems.",
        "startTime": 731,
        "endTime": 3359,
        "slowStartTime": 1247,
        "slowEndTime": 5263
    },
    {
        "text": "They often share certain characteristics which make them really good at their job.",
        "startTime": 3703,
        "endTime": 7541,
        "slowStartTime": 5705,
        "slowEndTime": 11537
    },
    {
        "text": "Frustration can be seen as a bad thing,...",
        "startTime": 8191,
        "endTime": 10008,
        "slowStartTime": 12437,
        "slowEndTime": 15237
    },
    {
        "text": "...but for design engineers, it can be the starting point for a really good idea.",
        "startTime": 10751,
        "endTime": 14171,
        "slowStartTime": 16277,
        "slowEndTime": 21482
    },
    {
        "text": "Identifying what frustrates you about an existing product can help you make it better.",
        "startTime": 15545,
        "endTime": 19763,
        "slowStartTime": 23468,
        "slowEndTime": 29869
    },
    {
        "text": "A successful and well-designed product is something that's easy to use.",
        "startTime": 20231,
        "endTime": 23661,
        "slowStartTime": 30497,
        "slowEndTime": 35716
    },
    {
        "text": "James Dyson's frustration with the vacuum bag encouraged him to rethink it...",
        "startTime": 24145,
        "endTime": 27899,
        "slowStartTime": 36368,
        "slowEndTime": 42073
    },
    {
        "text": "...and then use a cyclone design instead.",
        "startTime": 28045,
        "endTime": 30242,
        "slowStartTime": 42217,
        "slowEndTime": 45588
    },
    {
        "text": "Wrong thinking is allowing yourself to think differently...",
        "startTime": 30986,
        "endTime": 33525,
        "slowStartTime": 46629,
        "slowEndTime": 50512
    },
    {
        "text": "...and to not be afraid of trying new and crazy ideas.",
        "startTime": 33847,
        "endTime": 36585,
        "slowStartTime": 50920,
        "slowEndTime": 55102
    },
    {
        "text": "Keeping an open mind can lead to a solution that no one has ever thought of before.",
        "startTime": 37471,
        "endTime": 41232,
        "slowStartTime": 56356,
        "slowEndTime": 62073
    },
    {
        "text": "It's about thinking your way around a problem...",
        "startTime": 41314,
        "endTime": 43517,
        "slowStartTime": 62121,
        "slowEndTime": 65500
    },
    {
        "text": "...and seeing solutions that other people might not.",
        "startTime": 43609,
        "endTime": 45899,
        "slowStartTime": 65563,
        "slowEndTime": 69074
    },
    {
        "text": "To answer his brief of creating a small car that could still carry four adults,...",
        "startTime": 46384,
        "endTime": 50515,
        "slowStartTime": 69726,
        "slowEndTime": 75998
    },
    {
        "text": "...Alec Issigonis decided to put the engine in the opposite way round.",
        "startTime": 51017,
        "endTime": 54209,
        "slowStartTime": 76675,
        "slowEndTime": 81539
    },
    {
        "text": "A perfect design doesn't happen straightaway.",
        "startTime": 56966,
        "endTime": 59353,
        "slowStartTime": 85599,
        "slowEndTime": 89255
    },
    {
        "text": "Design is a process.",
        "startTime": 59621,
        "endTime": 60719,
        "slowStartTime": 89581,
        "slowEndTime": 91303
    },
    {
        "text": "When something doesn't work first time, it's about sticking with it,...",
        "startTime": 61455,
        "endTime": 64776,
        "slowStartTime": 92333,
        "slowEndTime": 97389
    },
    {
        "text": "...making small changes and ultimately, making your design stronger.",
        "startTime": 65086,
        "endTime": 68903,
        "slowStartTime": 97779,
        "slowEndTime": 103580
    },
    {
        "text": "You have to learn from things that went wrong,...",
        "startTime": 71508,
        "endTime": 73477,
        "slowStartTime": 107412,
        "slowEndTime": 110441
    },
    {
        "text": "...work out why they went wrong,...",
        "startTime": 73697,
        "endTime": 75080,
        "slowStartTime": 110695,
        "slowEndTime": 112845
    },
    {
        "text": "...and using that experience, find out how to make them better.",
        "startTime": 75175,
        "endTime": 78124,
        "slowStartTime": 112913,
        "slowEndTime": 117411
    },
    {
        "text": "It took Thomas Edison thousands of attempts to invent the light bulb.",
        "startTime": 78923,
        "endTime": 82371,
        "slowStartTime": 118534,
        "slowEndTime": 123782
    },
    {
        "text": "And now, it's still used by millions of people every day.",
        "startTime": 82656,
        "endTime": 85735,
        "slowStartTime": 124134,
        "slowEndTime": 128828
    },
    {
        "text": "All new designers need to have a bit of fighting spirit...",
        "startTime": 88217,
        "endTime": 90780,
        "slowStartTime": 132475,
        "slowEndTime": 136395
    },
    {
        "text": "...and be prepared to keep going in the face of competition.",
        "startTime": 90897,
        "endTime": 93777,
        "slowStartTime": 136495,
        "slowEndTime": 140890
    },
    {
        "text": "If you're designing a new product or improving someone else's,...",
        "startTime": 94041,
        "endTime": 96892,
        "slowStartTime": 141211,
        "slowEndTime": 145563
    },
    {
        "text": "...you have to convince people that your product is better.",
        "startTime": 97117,
        "endTime": 99912,
        "slowStartTime": 145826,
        "slowEndTime": 150093
    },
    {
        "text": "You'll have to explain your product clearly and talk passionately about it.",
        "startTime": 100445,
        "endTime": 103751,
        "slowStartTime": 150818,
        "slowEndTime": 155852
    },
    {
        "text": "Design engineers need to be determined.",
        "startTime": 103915,
        "endTime": 105971,
        "slowStartTime": 156023,
        "slowEndTime": 159181
    }
]